author: chfast
content: Quiz question: an account has no balance, 0 nonce, no code but storage. Is it considered "empty"? If considered empty, does it mean when touched it will be deleted?

author: chfast
content: Can the EIP-2930+ transaction have chain_id 0? Does it have special meaning?

author: sky.cactus
content: No, not per spec at least.  There was discussion around making 0 mean any chain, but people didn't like it.

author: sky.cactus
content: If you want to find out why, first place to check would be 2930 or 1559 EIP rationale sections.  Not sure if it is there, but it is where I would start.
